                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.6363/593: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Mexico</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Summerlin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-12-09T11:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 9, 1919, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received 7.24 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3354. Executive petroleum bill passed Mexican Senate yesterday.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Summerlin</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
